    "data": [
        {
            "title": "風流工︱每日自駕110公里成本¥100  河南「最強牛馬」月薪竟是……",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"董女士為了返工，每月駕車成本幾乎耗去一半人工。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/35559b3d2daebac8dc5ea284dc923e8a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031021413234878.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">董女士為了返工，每月駕車成本幾乎耗去一半人工。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>河南近日有女子自稱是「最強牛馬」，9年來每日自駕110公里來回，油資路費日耗100元人民幣。網民紛紛猜測女事主拿取多少「天價」月薪時，答案卻是僅得4640元，如此堅持長途跋涉通勤，原因是公司氣氛好，做得開心。\n\n</p><h2>網民猜是富二代或高管</h2>\n<p>據「都市報道」、《寧波晚報》等報道，董女士聲稱每日要自駕由家中到公司，來回車程達110公里。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕跨城上班。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e9bcd055f12493505dfbe6286c429bb/2025-03/62ec2493ly1hzboqdgaytj20j608ggmw_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕跨城上班。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女表示喜歡公司的氣氛，不介意每日長途駕車通勤。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c44cdb682c95f77248d4cda6ec5ff95/2025-03/526565656_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女表示喜歡公司的氣氛，不介意每日長途駕車通勤。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女表示喜歡公司的氣氛，不介意每日長途駕車通勤。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d27c4e2dc801536349336c736399ae5/2025-03/5262652623_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女表示喜歡公司的氣氛，不介意每日長途駕車通勤。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4698b9e0cf0884c0871813a34540b31c/2025-03/454545456564_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2dfa3b2456797564103d1a6631b18d79/2025-03/1545415461263_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86746af59110e6f922c298a2a62d1839/2025-03/1564564565643_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2dcbe5045d2716584625d88c2e77955a/2025-03/New_Project_444555_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        董女自稱是「最強牛馬」，每日自駕110公里跨城上班。抖音\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3436235/%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%A7%E5%8D%B7%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A56%E6%99%8220%E5%88%86%E4%B8%8B%E7%8F%AD-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%A0%E7%8F%AD\">反內卷︱網傳美的強制員工6時20分下班 網民：希望不是線上加班</a><br/>\n<br/>\n她指，每天早上7時18分便要出門，駕車由武收費站上高速路，從焦作嘉應觀收費站下，再走30分鐘左右的國道，往返路費40元，油費約50至60元，等於每天上班成本就高達100元。\n\n</p>\n<p>董女的通勤成本公開後，即引起網民好奇，指以董女一個月上班22天計，不算駕車時間，僅油費路費，便要2200元，還未計算汽車的維修成本。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3435981/%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%A7%E5%8D%B7%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%86%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%BE%E5%B7%A5-%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%8B%E9%83%A8%E6%AF%8F%E6%99%9A9%E6%99%82%E5%B7%A1%E6%9F%A5%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4\">反內卷︱大疆強制員工放工 人事部每晚9時巡查清場</a>\n</p>\n<p>網民紛紛猜測，董女家庭應是「有米一族」，或是女老闆一名，又或是企業高管，才會有本錢「打風流工」。\n\n</p>\n<p>不過，董女士澄清，自己只是普通「牛馬」，每月薪金只是4640元。她解釋，能堅持9年，不怕路遙在這間公司上班，是因為公司氣氛佳，自己特別喜歡，即使在疫情，公司也未曾拖欠員工一分錢人工，出於熱愛，所以一直也不怕交通開支大，每日通勤返工，沒有轉工念頭。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p><div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_box\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" is_mini=\"true\" style=\"background: initial !important; border: initial !important; border-radius: initial !important; border-spacing: initial !important; border-collapse: initial !important; direction: ltr !important; flex-direction: initial !important; font-weight: initial !important; height: initial !important; letter-spacing: initial !important; min-width: initial !important; max-width: initial !important; min-height: initial !important; max-height: initial !important; margin: auto !important; outline: initial !important; padding: initial !important; position: absolute; table-layout: initial !important; text-align: initial !important; text-shadow: initial !important; width: initial !important; word-break: initial !important; word-spacing: initial !important; overflow-wrap: initial !important; box-sizing: initial !important; display: initial !important; color: inherit !important; font-size: 13px !important; font-family: X-LocaleSpecific, sans-serif, Tahoma, Helvetica !important; line-height: 13px !important; vertical-align: top !important; white-space: inherit !important; left: 869px; top: 456px; opacity: 0.05;\">\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_logo\" title=\"翻譯選取的文字\"> </div>\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_sound\" title=\"朗讀\" title_play=\"朗讀\" title_stop=\"停止\"> </div>\n<div class=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini\" id=\"s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini_copy\" title=\"將文字複製到剪貼簿\"> </div>\n</div>\n<link href=\"moz-extension://e5e0c8cc-d50e-4025-a617-4623c74b4c06/skin/s3gt_tooltip_mini.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"/>\n<style media=\"print\" type=\"text/css\">\n\n\n\n\n\n#s3gt_translate_tooltip_mini { display: none !important; }\n\n/*--><!]]]]]]><![CDATA[><![CDATA[>*/\n\n\n\n\n</style>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
