            "title": "北海油輪與貨船相撞 英國正展開救援",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"英國海岸防衛隊直升機。 IG / maritimecoastguard\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/9968775ac0eec8420a1b810372cdec8e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031020465882204.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">英國海岸防衛隊直升機。 IG / maritimecoastguard</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>英國海岸防衛隊周一表示，一艘油輪與一艘貨船在英格蘭東部海岸相撞，救援行動正在進行中。\n\n</p>\n<p>海岸防衛隊於當地上午9時48分接報，消息指油輪起火。海岸防衛隊派出飛機和附近具有消防能力的船隻前往北海現場。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057392/即時-國際-北海油輪與貨船相撞-英國正展開救援",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 20:56:27",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海盈山單日沽5伙 高層海景戶呎價達2.79萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海盈山單日沽5伙，高層海景戶呎價達2.79萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2eba719b598770d581e7507b8bf68377/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031020450868231.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海盈山單日沽5伙，高層海景戶呎價達2.79萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>嘉里夥拍信和、太古地產及港鐵合作發展的黃竹坑站上蓋港島南岸新盤海盈山，單日沽5伙，套現約6,856.37萬元，成交價由1,077.42萬至1,715.22萬元，其中高層海景單位，成交呎價達27,981元。\n\n</p>\n<p>港島南岸第4期的海盈山分兩期發展，共提供800伙，現時推售的4A期，項目共提供432伙，面積351至1847方呎，涵蓋1房至4房戶型，主打2房戶佔逾60%。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
